metadata.name: Natura: Girl with a Pearl Earring
metadata.description:
Organic version of Vermeer´s “Girl with a Pearl Earring”.  
Created through digital collage using pressed flowers.  
3300px X 4200px  
350 DPI

In the Natura collection I combine classic artworks from ‘old masters’ with pressed flower art. Natura means essential character/identity, and it refers to our connectedness with nature.

This artwork is authentic and was created by dodsicle; the purchase of the NFT is a purchase of the asset, not of the copyright.
